{"tid":2097726,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"信和集團宣揚港獨，違反國安法，罪大惡極","createTime":"2020-07-07T04:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T09:48:07.000Z","uid":48040,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f4b0f414df3eacba49d7e7be88c05488365627d","tid":2097726,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"「中港城 China Hong Kong City」是信和集團旗下物業。<br />\n該名稱「中港（China Hong Kong）」，將中國及香港分庭抗禮，涉嫌鼓吹港獨，信和管理層可能會面臨終身監禁的懲罰。<br />\n我知，信和可能會解釋，「中港」意思是「中國的香港」。但如果真係咁，英文名稱應該係「Hong Kong China City」，因為英文是將小概念放前、大概念放後。例如中國北京的英文是Beijing China。<br />\n所以，好明顯，「中港城」意思絕對不是「中國的香港」，而是「中國和香港」，違反了國安法。<br />\n利申：信和本身就藍，所以要以紅制藍。<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTyuR4gnpUqs&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEqWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=71cc312d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs</a>"},{"pid":"4fb0b61855bff6156cb84deb3c6919854fc0ccaa","tid":2097726,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"222e2e74fd91a2fca66d8538f4ae38a3cc7c5910","tid":2097726,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"ching腦洞大開，歎為觀止"},{"pid":"a937f60a745354dac5b2cec9dc2681b90a8fcb63","tid":2097726,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"應該改名做中國城"},{"pid":"87d7352d504fc5711e15584881fe2b22bbc72081","tid":2097726,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"應該改名做中國中國香港城"},{"pid":"9d56defd7167a90e9f998966bdfa310cfb290565","tid":2097726,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"其實中國深圳陸路海關都犯法<br />\n根本唔應該叫中國邊檢<br />\n陸路海關連接香港<br />\n應該叫中國深圳邊檢<br />\n否則會被人誤認為香港唔係中國一部分<br />\n我地要鬥紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre